1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Velocitex is a 3D momentum puzzle game.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
You guide a candy through a machine,

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:10,000
using slopes, bounce, grip, braking, and timing to reach the cup.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Early rooms teach one idea at a time.

5
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Later rooms combine rails, pressure plates, moving platforms, cannons, and magnets into harder routes.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,000
It is a playable Windows game with candy customization,

7
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:29,000
achievements, accessibility settings, room-start saves, and Room Select.

8
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:34,000
Codex helped turn design decisions into Godot and C# code,

9
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:39,000
investigate movement and saving issues, and build repeatable tests.

10
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:45,000
GPT-5.6, used through Codex, helped reason through mechanics,

11
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:50,000
edge cases, and test coverage.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:57,000
Download Velocitex for Windows, and see how far your momentum can take you.
